data.description: Come and check out this beautiful 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo nestled in the heart of the Destin. This condo doesn't only offer style but it also offers convenience to the beach, shopping centers and grocery stores. This property is located on the 3rd floor (highest floor) facing away from the parking area and other buildings, providing one of the best views available. In 2019 this unit did get a new ac, water heater, new kitchen cabinets, new appliances, new vanities cabinets and counter tops in bathrooms. If this is a unit that you want to see, please don't hesitate to give Jay a call to schedule your showing today.
